    "However, to unlock the full potential of MLMs, they would need even more fine-grained feedback.",
    "The longer the answers get, the less an aggregated score summarizing the human preference for the answer helps.",
    "Promising future directions are to analyze ways to target the feedback to certain parts of the answer.",
    "Consider multi-hop reasoning for example.",
    "Was the first step already faulty, or was it the final conclusion that did not fit to the previous intermediate results, although these were correct?"
